mised myself after 2021 that I would give it everything for the three years to try and qualify for Paris and if it did not work out at least I would never look back and say I did not try my best.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.155752270964535e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"the three years\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I did and here I am going to the Olympics which is so exciting.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't leaving that unturned this year, because I did not want anyone to take my spot away.\\\"\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"my spot\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have two really strong relay teams' -Paris-bound Sharlene Mawdsley is targeting an Olympic medalpic.twitter.com/e6k3qKTJRp While she had not considered herself superstitious, she was leaving nothing to chance.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two really strong relay teams' -Paris-bound Sharlene Mawdsley\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medalpic.twitter.com/e6k3qKTJRp\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"chance\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Newport native warned her mother not to book any flights - \\\"of course she did it behind my back anyways\\\" - and purposefully avoided talking to her coach Gary Ryan abou