_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999795870335951, \"rank\": 2.0372329148674913e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adeleke\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"the fore\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic qualification\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"both the women\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"4x400m\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"what path\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletics schedule is bookended by the mixed relay and women's relay - the women's relay final on 10 August falls on Mawdsley's 26th birthday - so what that means for Adeleke in her quest for silverware in the individual event has been the subject of much discussion.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletics schedule\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed relay\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"women's relay\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's relay\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"10 August\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"Mawdsley's 26th birthday\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"Adeleke\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"her quest\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"silverware\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual event\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"the subject\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"much discussion\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having run five times in six days at the European Championships in Rome to collect silver (women's relay) and gold in the mixed relay, Mawdsley's outlook is pretty straight forward.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.9324154437394766, \"rank\": 0.07228780407035917, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six days\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"the European Championships\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"women's relay\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed relay\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2737}, {\"ngram\": \"Mawdsley's outlook\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will go out on the track as many times as I can,\\\" she insists, \\\"either before my individual event or after.\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"my individual event\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be an Olympian means everything, and I am a big team player, I love the relays.\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999258762, \"rank\": 7.395538024537144e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"a big team player\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"the relays\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I do not see why I would not do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With Ireland now firmly established as a relay force, how would she feel if Adeleke decided to skip an event to boost her own chances of success in a tight schedule?\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3029, \"end\": 3036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999795870335951, \"rank\": 2.0372329148674913e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a relay force\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"Adeleke\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3132}, {\"ngram\": \"her own chances\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"a tight schedule\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think Rhasidat has to make the decision that's best for her.\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rhasidat\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3208}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I would have no hard feelings at all.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no hard feelings\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think I am going to be challenging for a gold medal, not this year anyway, so I am not in that position to be able to say what I would do.\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3359}, {\"ngram\": \"that position\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I respect her decision regardless of what she does, of course we would absolutely love to have her on the team, that's no secret, but whatever she does is what's best for her.\\\"\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3475}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3514}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3563}, {\"ngram\": \"no secret\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3581}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mawdsley is looking to bring a little more of her relay fight to the individual party next month, with Rome a reminder of her capabilities with the bit between her teeth.\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3734, \"end\": 3738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.9324154437394766, \"rank\": 0.07228780407035917, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mawdsley\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3639}, {\"ngram\": \"her relay fight\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3692}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual party\", \"from\": 3696, \"to\": 3716}, {\"ngram\": \"a reminder\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"her capabilities\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3769}, {\"ngram\": \"the bit\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3782}, {\"ngram\": \"her teeth\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With gold in the bag from the mixed relay,Mawdsley ran a superb anchor leg (49.76)to power Ireland into the women's final as heat winners just a day afterher exploits in the 400m individual final (51.59).\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 4007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3894, \"end\": 3901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999795870335951, \"rank\": 2.0372329148674913e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3808, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"the bag\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3823}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixe