304, \"to\": 4319}, {\"ngram\": \"that extra edge\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4398}, {\"ngram\": \"a relay\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That little hunger, I see the finish line a lot sooner than in the individual.\\\"\", \"from\": 4421, \"to\": 4500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4462}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can she bring that steely determination into individual?\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that steely determination\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"individual\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's what we have been working on the past few weeks, the past few months.\", \"from\": 4560, \"to\": 4637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past few weeks\", \"from\": 4597, \"to\": 4615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are some races where I am coming out, 'yes, I did that', and other races where I am like, 'ooops, I forgot to do that today'.\", \"from\": 4638, \"to\": 4769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some races\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4658}, {\"ngram\": \"ooops\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's exciting that there are always things to improve on.\\\"\", \"from\": 4770, \"to\": 4828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next week she departs on a camp, the last gruelling hard block of training before Paris.\", \"from\": 4830, \"to\": 4918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4912, \"end\": 4917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.155752270964535e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a camp\", \"from\": 4855, \"to\":